    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dagger Froggy is a small roguelike with very simple gameplay, throw the dagger at enemies and retrieve it to defeat the next one!, try to survive for 10 minutes, creating incredible builds!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FACE INCREASINGLY POWERFUL ENEMIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The further you get, the more difficult enemies appear! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At each end of the horde you choose between 4 improvements, which will help you survive against these adorable creatures.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 30 Base Improvements, which combine with each other, making incredible Combos! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPECIALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you maximize an improvement, you release a Special. Each Special is unique and has effects that can improve your character or the daggers </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046050/extras/69c3d5a9dc62ba2fb1825aa4e2d185a4.poster.avif?t=1749758088\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046050/extras/69c3d5a9dc62ba2fb1825aa4e2d185a4.webm?t=1749758088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046050/extras/69c3d5a9dc62ba2fb1825aa4e2d185a4.mp4?t=1749758088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE FROGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each little frog has its own skills, so you can start with 2 points of some improvement, in addition to each one having its own unique style. 😎 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE SCENARIOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Scenario/Map has its own style and can be unlocked as soon as you win a match on the previous map. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the coins that fall from enemies, and those you earn after finishing a match, you can unlock improvement points, so you can start with some improvements now!</p>",
